		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_UNIT_LIBURNA_PEDIA">
			<Text>This light and fast hunter was a dominant ship of the Classical era. It originally had one bench with 25 oars on each side, while in later years it was equipped with two banks of oars (a bireme), faster, lighter, and more agile than triremes.</Text>
